data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4 bed, 2.5 bath 2-story residence boasts a spacious floor plan with a bonus 5th bedroom/office. The master suite is conveniently located on the main floor for your comfort. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, this home offers tranquility and safety. Enjoy the lush green views across the street from the park. Plenty of room in the spacious backyard for your pool or grilling space. For the budget minded consumer enjoy the energy savings provided by the roof top solar panels. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your forever home!
